How do you automate drop down in selenium in webdriver?

In Selenium webdriver provides a class known as select class
using that class it provides differnet methods
using those methods
we can select a value from a drop down 
using index, value, visible text
using these 3 diff ways, we can select a value from a DD
you can use only if tag name starts with select tag
if its starts with other tag such as input, button than
select class will not work

